---
title: Garlic & Sesame Beef Meatball Noodles with Stir-Fried Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: Put an Asian spin on beef meatballs with oyster sauce, sesame seeds and garlic. Then, swap the usual pasta for udon
noodles, add some tasty greens and you've got yourself a new speedy noodle dish that's sure to become a family fave.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-garlic-sesame-beef-noodles-954f1739.jpg
